    "The test converged r =.65 and r =.74 with other commercial verbal reasoning tests.",
    "Additionally, the test converged r =.58 with a verbal reasoning test from the International Cognitive Ability Resource (ICAR, 2014).",
    "The norm scores were derived from a sample of 38,896 real-world job applicants.",
    "The vast majority of applicants applied to jobs targeted toward applicants who were soon-tograduate or had recently graduated with Bachelor's degrees (98.67%), and applicants' mean age was 22.67 (SD = 4.25).",
